  "folder": "WjYphB21qHLl9NTH",
  "name": "Hair Whips",
  "type": "spell",
  "_id": "8dI9PGSghSs6l8xQ",
  "img": "systems/n5eb/assets/Icons%20%26%20Images/Clans/Otsutsuki.png",
  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>Your hair extends like tendrils from atop your head, waving and whipping around violently. As an action, you can send your strands of hair forward, doing one of the following:</p><ul data-start=\"177\" data-end=\"839\"><li data-start=\"177\" data-end=\"444\"><p data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"444\"><strong data-start=\"179\" data-end=\"199\">Piercing Attack:</strong> Sending several strands forward in a sharp point to pierce your enemies. Make a ranged Ninjutsu attack. On a hit, the target takes 3d8 + your Ninjutsu modifier in piercing damage. As an action on each of your turns, you can make another attack.</p></li><li data-start=\"448\" data-end=\"839\"><p data-start=\"450\" data-end=\"839\"><strong data-start=\"450\" data-end=\"471\">Restraint Attack:</strong> Your hair attempts to wrap around a creature's limbs like restraints, holding them in place. A creature must make a Strength saving throw. On a failure, they become restrained. A creature restrained this way takes 2d8 chakra damage at the start of their turn. A creature remakes their saving throw at the end of each of their turns, ending the restraint on a success.</p></li></ul><p data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"1012\" data-is-last-node data-is-only-node><strong data-start=\"841\" data-end=\"861\">At higher ranks:</strong> For each rank you cast this Jutsu above D-Rank, increase the cost by 3, the damage dealt by 1d8, or you can target an additional creature to restrain.</p>",
      "chat": ""
    },
